==Vision==

"I want and visualize and aspire toward a system of society and
learning where each person is able to rise to his or her fullest
potential without social or financial encumberance, where they may
express themselves fully and without reservation through art, writing,
athletics, invention, or even through their avocations or lifestyle.

Where they are able to form networks of meaningful and rewarding
relationships with their peers, with people who share the same
interests or hobbies, the same political or religious affiliations - or
different interests or affiliations, as the case may be.

This to me is a society where knowledge and learning are public goods,
freely created and shared, not hoarded or withheld in order to extract
wealth or influence.

This is what I aspire toward, this is what I work toward". 
&mdash; Stephen Downes, http://www.downes.ca/vision.htm

